{"tid":1546164,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"睇黎香港人仲未夠力量去同特區政府爭取任何野","createTime":"2019-09-06T07:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T08:39:46.000Z","uid":222614,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7f1f4e87b7c83b8e7cce061bd6ec7e37be9c881e","tid":1546164,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:33:40.000Z","msg":"淨係要佢撤回一項修訂，都要花費咁多人力物力時間同資源<br />\n<br />\n中間仲要衍生出各種問題，又有幾個義士死諫，無數兄弟受傷被捕<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下，一項修訂已經搞到我地咁傷<br />\n往後仲會有幾多次利用立法會去做啲咁黑暗既野？<br />\n<br />\n二百萬人又點？二百萬個零都只係零，係成個體制機器面對猶如樓蟻<br />\n<br />\n美國肯幫忙固然重要，但佢地有自己既取捨同時間表<br />\n而我地正處於一場人道危機，需要即時既支援<br />\n<br />\n事實係我地真係太弱，二百萬個弱者都只係一班弱者<br />\n<br />\n係暴政面前，人數唔係最重要，而係人既質素"},{"pid":"8ea998c22cc3bde8a8900b0e354a10d38a0c472d","tid":1546164,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:34:05.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr0Bo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=40d2e8e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"8d465f416537c19a64f4b6c50d84d473f0da5e7b","tid":1546164,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:34:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49d62b3e8fa8c73eaf48f61d2009522f2e280b8b","tid":1546164,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:34:12.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai